{"tid":2030470,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"曾志豪：現在佢無懼國際壓力，可見未來或有人於現場直接死亡！","createTime":"2020-05-22T18:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T19:22:44.000Z","uid":219007,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"009efac8e11ed9cf43afc4a311f349d4116262df","tid":2030470,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:29:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iCviegSvcQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiCviegSvcQA&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CC2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=763960f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iCviegSvcQA</a><br />\n<br />\n40:00<br />\n<br />\n好多人都講得啱，今次終於打大佬，得就得，唔得就死得。<br />\n<br />\n未來一連串抗爭日子，打壓將會比過往大。 <span style=\"color: red;\">因為佢哋而家想營造一個氣氛，就係香港將會出現一個好爆炸性嘅對抗！</span> 佢之前國安法流出後呼籲中資要小心，即係撩交嗌，係想營造一個會打鑊勁既，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢就係期望打一大鋪跟住就能夠靜落嚟。</span> 但我嗰日會照去，但要認清風險係比之前大好多！ 無錯「勇者無懼」 但真正既勇者係要考慮清楚先去做。<br />\n<br />\n依家打大佬，短兵相接，絕對係有機會出現流血，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係反送中嗰隻流血，係指喺戰場上直接死亡。 </span><span style=\"color: red;\">因為而家唔怕國際壓力外國制裁冇哂底線，雙方中間而家冇緩衝。 </span><br />\n<br />\n曼德拉嗰陣就算有死人，但最後都要經過十幾廿年先搵到出路，<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我哋一鋪晒冷係冇可能，亦都唔會一下子達到我地目的，靠呢幾次上街就成功係冇可能，真係要慢慢嚟。</span>"},{"pid":"615fd1b5edb5ba32694ea334b03589ecc6099178","tid":2030470,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbb7185d186c2d456ca1aa4ea6dc8792832dfee","tid":2030470,"uid":304769,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:33:22.000Z","msg":"正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span>"},{"pid":"3be7280908eae2d52914c11667181ee6781fec38","tid":2030470,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:34:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db7c68d32fb7b7ff9de9a941c323e1ed040c5856","tid":2030470,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:35:30.000Z","msg":"link up英國民意<br />\n並肩作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f457689548a48e27de8d0fdde4bb65353fbb81","tid":2030470,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:43:07.000Z","msg":"就算唔係聽日<br />\n終有一日中共會好多納粹屠殺猶太人咁對付香港人<br />\n就算戰敗前幾日都仲殺緊"},{"pid":"a939cc11c0166b5ff24cdc5cb0c94f6df3002b22","tid":2030470,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:51:14.000Z","msg":"本身都唔信你 遲早變新疆"},{"pid":"9a9402724fafbb0bfb120d499fe6cef349f03822","tid":2030470,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:54:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6f53a18c501377e2205e98c0ffb30aecce274863","tid":2030470,"uid":101307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:57:03.000Z","msg":"的確係 比定心理準備香港人 五毛們到時唔用送頭做藉口 直頭叫人放棄唔好得罪呀爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13c39a216dc790683e9310dc376679778abd044","tid":2030470,"uid":283668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T19:03:15.000Z","msg":"留返條命"},{"pid":"bc97b4e6f04051e0c112f3eba3fc254f8c26dcd8","tid":2030470,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{